# **1. ETABS / Prota / PDF / Archive Status**

**Status: ALL 7 ADAPTERS FULLY IMPLEMENTED**

Priority ranking and implementation baseline per IFS-BUILD-OUT3-PARSER-20260424 §2 (source priority). Each adapter inherits BaseParser and implements parse() + private _extract_* methods with normalized FieldExtraction output.

## **1.1 ETABS Adapter (P3)**

**Module:** etabs_parser/etabs_main.py | **Library:** openpyxl + pandas | **Priority Rank:** 3

| **Task** | **Description** | **Implementation Notes** | **Status** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| EP-01 | ETABSParser class — Excel workbook loader | Workbook opened via openpyxl; sheet discovery by name (SECTION, MEMBER, LOAD). Fallback to sheet index if names unavailable. _load_workbook() complete. | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| EP-02 | Sheet discovery → member / section tabs | Iterates through all sheets; identifies SECTION (F-063 primary), MEMBER (topology), LOAD (P2 fallback for missing MBS loads). Logs sheet mappings to INFO level. | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| EP-03 | Section schedule → F-063 (primary source) | Parses SECTION sheet for member ID, section name columns. Matches ISO 6162 / IS 808 catalogue. Known prefixes: UB, UC, RHS, SHS, CHS, IPE, HEA, HEB, WB, WC. IS808_LOOKUP_REQUIRED flag if not recognised. | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| EP-04 | Member topology → F-039, F-040 (grid) | MEMBER sheet parsed for joint X/Y/Z coordinates. Grid spacing derived as minimum positive Δ(X/Z). Bay count = unique X − 1. Topology map built (member_id → (joint_start, joint_end)). | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| EP-05 | Load schedule → P2 fallback for F-055/058 (floor/roof loads) | LOAD sheet parsed for distributed load values. Fallback role: if MBS P2 load absent, ETABS P3 supplies load with confidence 85. No confidence inflation for known values. | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| EP-06 | Confidence & source priority | All ETABS fields: source_type = ETABS, priority_rank = 3. Confidence: structured_keyword = 80 (openpyxl parsing; some ambiguity in sheet structure), table_lookup = 85 (load fallback from structured tab). Capped at 85 per hard rules. | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| EP-07 | Missing data handling | Absent load → UNRESOLVED + FB-RULE-025 flag (ETABS-specific fallback marker). Unmapped section → IS808_LOOKUP_REQUIRED + confidence reduced to 75. | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| EP-08 | Unit normalisation | ETABS units typically metric (mm/M). normalise_unit() handles variant scales. If unit ambiguous, flag: UNIT_CONVERSION_UNCERTAIN; confidence reduced to 70. | **IMPLEMENTED** |

**ETABS Source Priority:** PRIORITY_RANK = 3 (P3 authority; yields to STAAD P1 and MBS P2 in conflict)

**Key Risk (RISK-B5-01):** >20% of ETABS sections may be unmapped against IS 808 catalogue if project uses vendor-specific or legacy naming. Mitigation: IS808_LOOKUP_REQUIRED flag + Log warning; manual review escalated.

