## **1.2 Prota DXF Adapter (P4)**

**Module:** prota_parser/prota_parser.py | **Library:** ezdxf | **Priority Rank:** 4

| **Task** | **Description** | **Implementation Notes** | **Status** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| PP-01 | protaParser class — DXF file loader (geometry primary) | DXF loaded via ezdxf.readfile(). Entity iteration over LWPOLYLINE, INSERT, DIMENSION blocks. Member geometry extracted via layer/block metadata. _load_dxf() complete. | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| PP-02 | Coordinate extraction → F-039, F-040, F-172 (grid/bay) | Polylines and insertion points parsed for X/Z coordinates. Layer attributes inspected for grid labels. Bay spacing = min Δ(X/Z); bay count = unique X − 1. Geometry-only source. | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| PP-03 | Member incidences → topology inference (geometry-driven) | Connects entities by spatial proximity (threshold: 10mm). Builds self._topology for member_id → (x_start, y_end). Topology is DERIVED from geometry; not explicit. Status flag: DERIVED (not structured_keyword). | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| PP-04 | Cross-section lookup → F-063 (geometry hints, not direct) | Dimension blocks may encode section size hint (e.g. "100×50" in text label). Parsed via RE_DIMENSION_LABEL regex. Confidence reduced to 65 (derived + uncertain parsing). IS808_LOOKUP_REQUIRED flag set to require catalogue lookup. | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| PP-05 | Support/restraint → F-045, F-046, F-047 (from layer/block) | Support points marked in DXF by layer name (SUPPORTS, FIXED, PINNED). Coordinates extracted; length/width/height derived from bounding box. Status: DERIVED. | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| PP-06 | Load data ABSENT in DXF | DXF is geometry-only format. Load fields (F-055, F-058) not populated; status: UNRESOLVED. Flag: FB-RULE-026 (PROTA_DXF_LOAD_ABSENT). Fallback chain: ETABS P3 → Manual→DE. | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| PP-07 | Connection & bolt data ABSENT | Connection type (F-075) and bolt table (F-081–F-089) not in DXF. Status: UNRESOLVED for all bolt fields. Flags: FB-RULE-015 (connection absent), FB-RULE-013/014 (bolt fields absent). Confidence: 0. | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| PP-08 | Confidence & source priority | All Prota DXF fields: source_type = PROTA_DXF, priority_rank = 4. Confidence: derived = 65 (geometry inference); IS808 section hints = 65. Hard cap: 75 per FieldExtraction contract. | **IMPLEMENTED** |

**Prota DXF Source Priority:** PRIORITY_RANK = 4 (P4 authority; yields to STAAD P1, MBS P2, ETABS P3)

**Key Risk (RISK-B5-02):** Geometry-only source means member identification is spatial proximity–based. If DXF is poorly attributed or uses non-standard layer naming, topology may be incomplete or incorrect. Mitigation: Log all spatial matches; DERIVED status signals manual review requirement.

