## **1.3 Prota PDF Adapter (P5)**

**Module:** prota_parser/prota_parser.py | **Library:** pdfplumber | **Priority Rank:** 5

| **Task** | **Description** | **Implementation Notes** | **Status** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| PP-09 | protaPDFParser — PDF document loader | pdfplumber.open() reads Prota CAD export (often 2D drawings + tabular data). Page iteration + table extraction via pdfplumber.extract_tables(). | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| PP-10 | Tabular data extraction → section schedule | Tables on pages identified via table region detection. Columns matched to section name, quantity. Section name extracted via RE_SECTION_NAME_PDF regex. Confidence: 70 (PDF text; OCR not used). | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| PP-11 | Grid / bay extraction from drawing annotations | PDF may contain grid labels in text or table form. Parsed via table extraction + regex. Bay spacing and count derived as in DXF adapter (min Δ, count unique X). Confidence: 70. | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| PP-12 | Load data from load summary table (if present) | If Prota PDF contains load schedule, extracted via table lookup. Confidence: 75 (structured table in PDF). If absent → UNRESOLVED + FB-RULE-027 (PROTA_PDF_LOAD_ABSENT); fallback chain: ETABS P3 → Manual→DE. | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| PP-13 | Connection & bolt data ABSENT in typical Prota PDF | Prota PDF export typically omits bolt schedule. Status: UNRESOLVED for F-075, F-081–F-089. Flags: FB-RULE-015/013/014. Confidence: 0. Fallback: Manual→DE. | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| PP-14 | PDF-specific guards | PDF confidence hard cap ≤ 85 enforced at FieldExtraction.__post_init__(). OCR not used (P7 task). Historical prohibition guard (P8) not triggered (P5 is structured text, not OCR). | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| PP-15 | Confidence & source priority | All Prota PDF fields: source_type = PROTA_PDF, priority_rank = 5. Confidence: structured_table = 75; regex_text = 70. Hard cap: 85. | **IMPLEMENTED** |

**Prota PDF Source Priority:** PRIORITY_RANK = 5 (P5 authority; yields to P1–P4)

**Key Risk (RISK-B5-03):** If Prota PDF absent entirely from project (AB blocked path), lane defers to ETABS P3 + Manual→DE. Mitigation: FB-RULE-027 flag surfaces gap; EvidenceExporter captures UNRESOLVED status.

