## **1.4 DWG/DXF Generic Adapter (P6)**

**Module:** cad_parser/cad_main.py | **Library:** ezdxf + ODA File Converter | **Priority Rank:** 6

| **Task** | **Description** | **Implementation Notes** | **Status** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| DP-01 | CADParser class — DWG/DXF multi-format support | Detects file extension (.dwg, .dxf). DWG files converted to DXF via ODA File Converter CLI before processing. Conversion output validated. _convert_dwg_to_dxf() and _load_dxf() complete. | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| DP-02 | ODA File Converter integration | System call to ODA converter: `oda_convert <input.dwg> <output.dxf> <options>`. Conversion failure → ESCALATE_IT + warning logged. DWG → DXF conversion lossless for geometry; some metadata may be lost. | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| DP-03 | Geometry extraction post-conversion | Post-conversion DXF processed identically to Prota DXF (DP-02 through DP-08). Entity iteration, coordinate extraction, layer/block inspection. | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| DP-04 | Confidence & risk flagging | DWG converted: confidence reduced by 5 points vs native DXF (conversion uncertainty). Base confidence 60 (geometry + conversion + uncertainty). Hard cap 75. Flag: DWG_CONVERTED_FROM_BINARY if conversion occurred. | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| DP-05 | ODA R14 compatibility check | ODA File Converter known issue: R14 files may lose some entity types (rare). If conversion detects truncation, log WARNING and set flag: ODA_R14_LOSS_POSSIBLE. Confidence reduced to 50. | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| DP-06 | Cross-platform path handling | ODA converter paths vary by OS (Windows: C:\Program Files\ODA\...; Linux: /opt/oda/...). Environment variable ODA_PATH checked at startup. If not found, raise RuntimeError with R-PARSER-01 reference. | **IMPLEMENTED** |
| DP-07 | Source priority & fallback chain | source_type = DWG_DXF_GENERIC, priority_rank = 6. Yields to STAAD (P1), MBS (P2), ETABS (P3), Prota DXF (P4), Prota PDF (P5). Missing fields same as Prota DXF (load, connection, bolt → UNRESOLVED). | **IMPLEMENTED** |

**DWG/DXF Source Priority:** PRIORITY_RANK = 6 (P6 authority; yields to P1–P5)

**Key Risk (RISK-B5-04):** ODA R14 file conversion may lose entity types. Mitigation: ODA_R14_LOSS_POSSIBLE flag + confidence reduction to 50. R-PARSER-01 ensures ODA installation verified before Block 5 coding; if missing, CADParser._check_oda_installed() raises RuntimeError at parse time.

