# **4. Risks / Gaps**

| **Risk ID** | **Description** | **Source** | **Severity** | **Mitigation** | **Status** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **RISK-B5-01** | ETABS >20% section unmapped against IS 808 catalogue | ETABS (P3) | **HIGH** | IS808_LOOKUP_REQUIRED flag + reduced confidence (75) + manual review escalation | **MONITORED** |
| **RISK-B5-02** | Prota DXF geometry-only; spatial proximity topology may be incorrect if DXF poorly attributed | Prota DXF (P4) | **MEDIUM** | DERIVED status signals manual review; log all spatial matches | **MONITORED** |
| **RISK-B5-03** | Prota PDF absent from project → AB blocked path | Prota PDF (P5) | **MEDIUM** | FB-RULE-027 flag; fallback to ETABS P3 + Manual→DE | **MONITORED** |
| **RISK-B5-04** | ODA R14 file conversion may lose entity types; cross-platform path issues | DWG/DXF (P6) | **MEDIUM** | ODA_R14_LOSS_POSSIBLE flag + confidence reduction (50); R-PARSER-01 ensures installation verified | **MONITORED** |
| **RISK-B5-05** | PDF Text regex parsing vulnerable to PDF encoding errors and layout variation | PDF Text (P7) | **MEDIUM** | Confidence capped at 65; conflict resolver prevents override; marked as fallback-only | **MONITORED** |
