## **Block 6 Agent Start Conditions**

- BaseParser and all 7 adapters frozen — do not modify; inherit only if extending.

- All adapters produce normalized FieldExtraction objects with correct source_type, priority_rank, confidence_score, extraction_method, status, and flags.

- ParserOutput container and evidence_automation/evidence_exporter.py are stable APIs.

- Verify handling for following scenarios (documented in test stubs T-PARSE-01 through T-PARSE-12):
  - **T-PARSE-01:** STAAD P1 bolt table complete → F-081–F-089 POPULATED, confidence 90
  - **T-PARSE-02:** STAAD P1 bolt table absent → F-081–F-089 UNRESOLVED, FB-RULE-013/014, confidence 0
  - **T-PARSE-03:** STAAD P1 connection type not explicit → F-075 UNRESOLVED, FB-RULE-015, confidence 0
  - **T-PARSE-04:** MBS P2 built-up section (PL+digits) → F-063 UNRESOLVED, FB-RULE-021, BUILDUP_PLATE_REQUIRED flag
  - **T-PARSE-05:** ETABS P3 load fallback (MBS absent) → F-055/058 POPULATED, confidence 85, extraction_method: fallback
  - **T-PARSE-06:** PDF Text P7 section guess (regex) → F-063 POPULATED, confidence 60, extraction_method: text_regex
  - **T-PARSE-07:** PDF Image P8 governing field → F-001 UNRESOLVED, HISTORICAL_PROHIBITED flag, confidence 0
  - **T-PARSE-08:** Conflict: STAAD P1 vs MBS P2 same F-field → conflict_resolver picks P1 (priority_rank=1 wins rank=2)
  - **T-PARSE-09:** Conflict: STAAD P1 vs PDF Text P7 → conflict_resolver picks P1; P7 never overrides P1–P6
  - **T-PARSE-10:** Fallback: ETABS P3 load (missing MBS) → confidence reduction + fallback flag; candidate for Manual→DE
  - **T-PARSE-11:** Unit normalisation: "1234mm", "1.234M", "KG500" → numeric string + confidence 95 (structured)
  - **T-PARSE-12:** Confidence hard caps applied: PDF_TEXT reduced to 85, PDF_IMAGE reduced to 75 if exceeded

- B-PARSER-01 clearance enables conflict_resolver.py (C9) design handoff for Block 6 conflict harness

- Do NOT proceed with write_to_db() testing in Block 6 until B-PARSER-02 cleared (DB tables exist).

